sequenceDiagram
participant C as Client
participant E as Edge/API
participant D as Messaging Domain
participant P as PostgreSQL
participant R as PubSub
C->>E: send(client_message_id, content)
E->>D: SubmitMessage
D->>P: transaction(sequence + message + jobs)
P-->>D: committed
D-->>E: canonical id + sequence
E-->>C: accepted
D->>R: broadcast committed event
R-->>C: message.created
